snippet.title: Gondola's Adventure | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for the game Gondola's Adventure, available on Steam in early 2021. Gondola's Adventure is a 2D precision platformer.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1473540/Gondolas_Adventure/
